                        <p>Items of claim exclusive of loss by fall of price of salt as I understand
                            it.</p>
                        <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Lord Lyons</hi>, <hi rend="italic">British
                                Minister at Washington.</hi>
                        </p>
